title: ModelsTied Photo Sets #2
description:
James Bertoni / Modelstied photos #2

30 thumb nail index jpg files & 7 WinRAR archives Use WinRAR to unpack the archives.

About 6,000 photos in 7 archive files, these are photo sets, not a mass of unrelated pictures. Each archive is independent, so if you want "Lara-Soft" but none of the others, the file will unpack without the other RAR files. (assuming you torrent program allows you to pick the files you want, like Bit-Torrent)


There are some incomplete sets the in the "Themes" file, sorry about that, it's how I found them.
The Code-Fetish, Posh-Iia, Lara-Soft, Womans Order are web site names found on the photos, all are JB's work. 
Code-Fetish & Posh-Iia are latex fetish photos, no bondage.
Lara-Soft is a couple of bondage - adventure theme sets.
Womans Order is femdom, unfortunitly only a couple of the sets are complete.

These came from usenet - news group: alt.binaries.pictures.erotica.fetish.latex, so if you frequent that group take note so you don't end up downloading 100's of file you already have. (tip o'the hat to Molle-999 for the original posts in news)

Bertoni rocks, these are great photos, enjoy.  ls
